	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CADANCE_DEFEATED_1">
			<Text>Shining...Please....He..lp.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CADANCE_DEFEATED_2">
			<Text>I'm sorry Celestia, I was not strong enough.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CADANCE_EXPANSION_SERIOUS_WARNING_1">
			<Text>As much as I believe we can all lived together peacefully, your settling near the Crystal Empire will no doubt cause trouble between us. Can I trust you to stop?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CADANCE_FIRSTGREETING_1">
			<Text>Hail and welcome, I am the Crystal Princess Cadance, and this is my husband, Shining Armor. I hope that we can love and tolerate each other, though if you wish to harm my subjects I and my husband will be quick to defend them.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CADANCE_GREETING_HOSTILE_HELLO_1">
			<Text>I knew there was a reason the Honor Guard were here. What do you want?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CADANCE_GREETING_NEUTRAL_HELLO_1">
			<Text>Hello, I am sorry that I can't entertain your arrival for too long, I am busy with renevating the palace, whoever designed this place put in one too many staircases.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CADANCE_GREETING_POLITE_HELLO_1">
			<Text>Hello, friend. The Crystal Festival is in full swing and Shining is about to joust. Do you have time to watch?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CADANCE_HOSTILE_AGGRESSIVE_MILITARY_WARNING_1">
			<Text>I have dispatched the Honor Guard to meet your troops amassing along our boarders. I trust that you'll call them back, as well I if you do.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CADANCE_OPEN_BORDERS_EXCHANGE_1">
			<Text>Our two kingdoms would benefit greatly from open travel between us. My people have many wears and an over abundance of flugelhorns to trade.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CADANCE_RESPONSE_REQUEST_1">
			<Text>I have an urgent request. Your assistance would not go unnoticed. You see, Shining kinda...Misplaced something.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CADANCE_LUXURY_TRADE_1">
			<Text>My subjects do love seeing exotic goods from far away lands. You see they've been locked away for a thousand years. We have many things we can trade for. Would this work?</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>


