		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CIVILOPEDIA_LEADERS_CADANCE_TEXT_1">
			<Text>Cadance's origins remain somewhat of mystery. Where she is from is unknown but it is known she grew up in Canterlot eventually foalsitting for Twilight Sparkle. She would go on to marry Twilight's brother, Shining Armor. During their marriage, the changlings led by Queen Chrysalis, invaded Canterlot. THe Queen used her shapeshifting powers to impersonate Cadance in a plot to feed teh changelings all the love in Equestria. Candance was freed by Twilight and her friends and later defeated the Queen. After Cadance's and Shining Armor's marriage, Princess Celestia task them both to protect teh Crystal Empire.</Text>
		</Row>
